Remarks: This is the description file for assignment 2 Question 1 & 2.

Operation procedure on Terminal:
	1. Input `make q1` to build `a2q1.c`, `make q2` to build `a2q2.c`, `make` or `make all` to build both of the c files.
	2. Input `./a2q1 cat` to run the program `a1q1.c`.
	3. Input `./a2q2 1` or `./a2q2 2` to run the program `a2q2.c`. The argument 1 represents that the parent process sends 2 of SIGUSR1 to the child process, and the argument 2 represents that the parent process send 2 different signals (SIGUSR1 and SIGUSR2) to the child process.
	4. To remove the executables, input `make clean`.
	5. The file `MyReport.md` contains my answers for the 2 questions.